 /dev/null is an independent data science consultant and instructor.<br>He enjoys visualizing data, implementing machine learning models, and building solutions using Python, R, JavaScript, and Bash.<br>Jeroen manages , a training and coaching firm that organizes open enrollment workshops, in-company courses, inspiration sessions, hackathons, and meetups.<br>Previously, he was an
